item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Network_Directory_Listing
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Network_Directory_Listing Datatype Description SoftLayer_Container_Network_Directory_Listing represents a single entry in a listing of files within a remote directory. API methods that return remote directory listings typically return arrays of SoftLayer_Container_Network_Directory_Listing objects. Local fileCount If the file in a directory listing is a directory itself then fileCount is the number of files within the directory. Type: integer name The name of a directory or a file within a directory listing.
